sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AI as AI Platform
    participant Hook as Traceability Hook
    participant Cmd as /arckit:traceability
    participant Template as Template System
    participant Files as File System
    
    User->>AI: /arckit:traceability PROJECT=001
    
    Note over AI,Hook: UserPromptSubmit Event
    AI->>Hook: Trigger traceability-scan.mjs
    Hook->>Files: Scan ARC-*-REQ-*.md
    Files-->>Hook: Requirement IDs extracted
    Hook->>Files: Scan ADRs, HLDs, DLDs, reviews
    Files-->>Hook: Requirement references extracted
    Hook->>Hook: Compute coverage by category/priority
    Hook->>Hook: Identify orphan requirements
    Hook->>Hook: Identify design-only references
    Hook->>Files: Check existing TRAC version
    Files-->>Hook: Version found (v1.0)
    Hook->>Hook: Suggest next version (v1.1)
    Hook-->>AI: Inject structured traceability data
    
    Note over AI,Cmd: Command Execution
    AI->>Cmd: Execute with pre-computed data
    Cmd->>Cmd: Use hook's requirements table
    Cmd->>Cmd: Use hook's coverage summary
    Cmd->>Cmd: Use hook's orphan lists
    
    Note over Cmd,Files: Selective File Reading
    Cmd->>Files: Read vendor HLD/DLD for component names
    Files-->>Cmd: Component/module descriptions
    Cmd->>Template: Load traceability-matrix-template.md
    Template-->>Cmd: Template content
    
    Note over Cmd: Build Traceability Matrix
    Cmd->>Cmd: Map requirements to design (from hook)
    Cmd->>Cmd: Map design to implementation (from prose)
    Cmd->>Cmd: Map implementation to tests
    Cmd->>Cmd: Calculate traceability score
    Cmd->>Cmd: Generate gap analysis
    Cmd->>Cmd: Create action items
    
    Note over Cmd,Files: Write Output
    Cmd->>Files: Write ARC-001-TRAC-v1.1.md (800+ lines)
    Files-->>Cmd: Write complete
    
    Cmd-->>AI: Summary only (not full content)
    AI-->>User: Coverage: 85/100, 3 critical gaps
